# Social Media Content Directory

This directory contains scripts for posting to social media platforms (Twitter/X, LinkedIn, Medium).

## Quick Start

See [TWITTER-IMPLEMENTATION-SUMMARY.md](./TWITTER-IMPLEMENTATION-SUMMARY.md) for complete Twitter setup.

## Installation

```bash
npm install twitter-api-v2
```

## Usage

```bash
# Preview thread (no posting)
npx tsx scripts/content-social/post-to-twitter.ts --dry-run

# Post to Twitter
npx tsx scripts/content-social/post-to-twitter.ts
```

